<item chapterid="602037" siteid="0" sourceid="0" sourcecid="0" sourcecorder="0" articleid="1938" articlename="一号红人" volumeid="0" posterid="1" poster="admin" postdate="1521786674" lastupdate="1521786674" chaptername="第030章节目标人选" chapterorder="31" size="6148" saleprice="0" salenum="0" totalcost="0" attachment="" summary="    章华也宽了心，“不知王部长看上我们这里哪个干部了？这可是我们十面镇干部的脸面啊。”

