<item chapterid="602121" siteid="0" sourceid="0" sourcecid="0" sourcecorder="0" articleid="1938" articlename="一号红人" volumeid="0" posterid="1" poster="admin" postdate="1521786674" lastupdate="1521786674" chaptername="第113章节两个好处" chapterorder="115" size="6109" saleprice="0" salenum="0" totalcost="0" attachment="" summary="    大家笑起来，高成汉却一本正经，“大家别笑，我说的是实话，就是这么回事。但这么做，至少有两个好处：

