<item chapterid="602156" siteid="0" sourceid="0" sourcecid="0" sourcecorder="0" articleid="1938" articlename="一号红人" volumeid="0" posterid="1" poster="admin" postdate="1521786674" lastupdate="1521786674" chaptername="第147章节电梯惊魂" chapterorder="150" size="6278" saleprice="0" salenum="0" totalcost="0" attachment="" summary="    胡小英笑着点点头道：“你这人很坦诚。”

